  <brief_title>Mechanical Plaque Control and Gingivitis Reduction in Fixed Appliance Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Mechanical Plaque Control and Gingivitis Reduction in Fixed Appliance Patients: Comparison of Different Toothbrushing Protocols</official_title>
  <sponsors>
