  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether the use of a sonic toothbrush alone is more
      effective than two other toothbrushing protocols on dental plaque elimination in patients
      with fixed orthodontic appliances.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
